\">http://service.sony.com.tw/i-manual/cht/hx750/c_digi_europe_co_dpsorting.html</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mpweekly.com/entertainment/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/%E5%AE%B6%E6%9C%89%E5%9B%8D%E4%BA%8B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpweekly.com%2Fentertainment%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%259B%258D%25E4%25BA%258B.png&h=d2940324&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當然我都好贊成大家刪埋81台啦，但如果長輩無電視睇會大嗌「世界末日」嘅，揀定節目，較時間自動轉台，避開晒CCTVB新聞時段 <span style=\"font-size: small;\">(節目中間新聞提要避唔開無辦法)</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Set埋自動定時收看31、77、99台新聞，為家人消毒</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">31台新聞 - 10:30pm<br />\n77台新聞 - 6-9am*, 12:30nn, 7:00pm, 11:30pm<br />\n99台新聞 - 6-9am*, 12:00nn, 6:00pm, 7:00pm<br />\n*Mon-Fri</span><br />\n通常電視都會彈嘅notice問你轉唔轉台，教埋佢哋搖控撳 &quot;ok&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<strong>以上只係抵制CCTVB一小步，最重要係下面幅圖！</strong>"},{"pid":"bec2c9d877ae0cf059fedf1fe092c887de2e9177","tid":1256903,"uid":267969,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:21:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/8tHsKku.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8tHsKku.jpg&h=1e1bda37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【緊急，有圖廣傳】終極抵制 CCTVB 行動整合 --&gt; 刪台、爭取有線Now開台、罷買！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1256133/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1256133/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"9efb2e3d3aa6e400f71795edb11aa3151cf8f399","tid":1256903,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:35:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30a63c1aaf35037cd184b0c4476e52293c7cf23f","tid":1256903,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-25T09:47:18.000Z","msg":"你今日刪咗83台未？"},{"pid":"57a6ba80b3eb00ce1ce6c9081c1bddcbe594f7f4","